<body>
    <h1>Incident Analysis: Unintended SMS/LINE Messages Sent to 70,000 Cust=
omers Due to Data Update Error</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"b0d6eb198a00" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/=
LINEMessagesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-Executivesummary(max5=
bullets)">Executive summary (max 5 bullets)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"4afc9076f858">
<li local-id=3D"b9d48c462105">
<p local-id=3D"d572e4c09235"><strong>Root cause (most likely):</strong> A <=
strong>bad customer data update</strong> entered the batch input, and the b=
atch-to-notification flow <strong>did not validate recipient eligibility/vo=
lume</strong>, allowing mass outbound messages to be generated.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc8184d3dd62">
<p local-id=3D"6981865fe592"><strong>Detection gap:</strong> The incident a=
ppears <strong>more consistent with reactive detection</strong> (business/c=
ustomer signals) than automated detection; similar historical records show =
<strong>missing/insufficient ordering, logging, and integrity checks</stron=
g> in batch/SMS pipelines (see <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://m=
anulife.service-now.com/problem.do?sysparm_query=3Dnumber=3DPRB00023122" re=
l=3D"nofollow"><strong>PRB00023122</strong></a>, <a class=3D"external-link"=
 href=3D"https://manulife.service-now.com/problem.do?sysparm_query=3Dnumber=
=3DPRB00022754" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>PRB00022754</strong></a>).</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"cce57de5c497">
<p local-id=3D"5330d3a60f79"><strong>Key risk:</strong> Without automated p=
re-send validation and suppression, the <strong>next batch run can re-trigg=
er</strong> mass messaging from another incorrect update.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1845e28846e8">
<p local-id=3D"d3222a1efb57"><strong>Immediate fix:</strong> Add a <strong>=
hard =E2=80=9Cmessage suppression / circuit breaker=E2=80=9D</strong> and <=
strong>recipient-volume guardrails</strong> before the next batch window.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bf1df85df571">
<p local-id=3D"1dc74fc01249"><strong>Strategic improvement:</strong> Implem=
ent <strong>end-to-end observability</strong> for batch =E2=86=92 data inte=
grity =E2=86=92 message generation with <strong>actionable alerts</strong> =
and <strong>L1/L2 runbooks</strong> aligned to =E2=80=9Cshift from user-rep=
orted to automated detection=E2=80=9D.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d5e3a73a46a1">
<h2 local-id=3D"f68a7f2898f0" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-1)Incidentcontext(fromyourbri=
ef)">1) Incident context (from your brief)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"735c5f594e08">
<li local-id=3D"cd997e0d1e82">
<p local-id=3D"1a994c30761c"><strong>Incident:</strong> <a class=3D"externa=
l-link" href=3D"https://manulife.service-now.com/incident.do?sysparm_query=
=3Dnumber=3DINC08574374" rel=3D"nofollow">INC08574374</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0508654343ca">
<p local-id=3D"991360386480"><strong>Summary:</strong> Unintended SMS/LINE =
messages sent to ~70,000 customers due to incorrect data update during batc=
h processing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"630920984d06">
<p local-id=3D"cc6c4f9d8b40"><strong>Impact:</strong> Customer confusion, c=
all center congestion, service degradation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b1623e41503">
<p local-id=3D"0ff5748b10df"><strong>Current status:</strong> Data correcte=
d; root cause under investigation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"083dea28f9c1">
<h2 local-id=3D"d90496059e6e" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-2)MTTxanalysis(best-effortwit=
havailableevidence)">2) MTTx analysis (best-effort with available evidence)=
</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"b270412312e6" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-MTTD(Detection)">MTTD (Detect=
ion)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"99b8f0168b59"><strong>Detection timeline (table)</strong></p=
>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"14=
914ff55dd9" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2078dd5fb949">
<th data-local-id=3D"7477108123ee" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"48e06dca1413">Step</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"e9c071e74881" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"4675afde9482">What happened</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f108a773614a" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"fca6222e5ca0">Evidence available</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"46128097ebdf">
<td data-local-id=3D"956ddb095d07" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"de2eadd6f475">Fault injection</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"38497c652560" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9bef9f2787f9">Incorrect data update enters batch input</p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bffc89fc024a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cfa18c9d1022">From incident summary</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c13065f40ce2">
<td data-local-id=3D"17642d148b51" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"af69ab61901d">Propagation</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"50baef134239" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9254146c92d1">Batch generates outbound SMS/LINE at scale</p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d159524101af" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"839eb490e067">From incident summary</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7ca768be12cf">
<td data-local-id=3D"5c7b42b69887" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d82195015f6d">Detection</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b0c200dfc7b9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1d00a23a8daf">Detected after messages were sent (likely via =
business/customer impact)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"116aa4eebd38" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"774663feceb5">No monitoring alert evidence found in retrieve=
d sources</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"74e2c0ab245b"><strong>Detection failure points</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ef02eb7d7ccd">
<li local-id=3D"bbc2ce9fbe1c">
<p local-id=3D"e26502fdab46"><strong>No automated =E2=80=9Cvolume anomaly=
=E2=80=9D detection</strong> on outbound messages (e.g., sudden spike to te=
ns of thousands).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5c16b8def89">
<p local-id=3D"22f48e60b1de"><strong>No automated =E2=80=9Cdata integrity=
=E2=80=9D detection</strong> on the upstream customer dataset change that f=
ed the batch.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9f2be076935c">
<p local-id=3D"33befbe58032"><strong>Insufficient traceability</strong> bet=
ween batch records and outbound notifications (a recurring theme in <a clas=
s=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://manulife.service-now.com/problem.do?sys=
parm_query=3Dnumber=3DPRB00023122" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>PRB00023122</st=
rong></a>: recommendation to include notification IDs in logs and enforce d=
eterministic ordering).</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"55063f697d02"><strong>Required monitoring signals not in pla=
ce (to meet =E2=80=9Cshift from user-reported to automated detection=E2=80=
=9D)</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a62034a973a1">
<li local-id=3D"835f50f17f98">
<p local-id=3D"c4433fd58c17"><strong>Outbound message rate + unique-recipie=
nt spike alert</strong> (per channel: SMS, LINE).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bea1c3192c44">
<p local-id=3D"419b589e1c61"><strong>Pre-send validation failure metric</st=
rong> (count of blocked messages, reasons).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ac76110c6cd">
<p local-id=3D"022e8d6f4e1c"><strong>Batch input delta checks</strong> (une=
xpected changes in recipient flags/segments).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"15f5c5c8acb8">
<p local-id=3D"7835e72c73b4"><strong>Correlation IDs</strong> from batch re=
cord =E2=86=92 notification ID =E2=86=92 delivery provider response (explic=
itly recommended in <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://manulife.ser=
vice-now.com/problem.do?sysparm_query=3Dnumber=3DPRB00023122" rel=3D"nofoll=
ow"><strong>PRB00023122</strong></a>).</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"564b1097e084">
<h3 local-id=3D"98de1321c7d5" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-MTTC(Containment)">MTTC (Cont=
ainment)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"646004576cd3"><strong>Containment steps &amp; timing (table)=
</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f4=
4ffc577462" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"cafa16c686a4">
<th data-local-id=3D"353ee684540f" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"86c178c2c205">Step</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"49bc0840ac5b" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d03485a5ec96">Containment action</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"9ae1a1ede5dd" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"37a88f0b817f">Manual vs automated</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"5b4305dbb0b9" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3f5235ad92b6">Evidence available</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f6205cb0600c">
<td data-local-id=3D"3fb916544e4d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fdfe230074d4">Stop further sends</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d2df1290630a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cccf48ab7d17">Suppress/stop message generation or downstream=
 dispatch</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a52c2b4d723f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5a7e326ad34e">Likely manual</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"55d4fcc86d6d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"52dd4d8a9021">Not evidenced in sources; inferred from =E2=80=
=9Cdata corrected=E2=80=9D status</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4208badabf58">
<td data-local-id=3D"e2930981433c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2a9d5e171805">Limit blast radius</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6427632ee056" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"90e7a0ac4f0b">Disable specific campaign/template or recipien=
t segment</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"34eeb722f69e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b3f82752a298">Likely manual</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1d655e4f4669" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a6fd820a5399">Not evidenced</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"abfb174444db">
<td data-local-id=3D"71b51b2474b7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e2833e22dc7d">Escalation</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"62a06081a66b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"49ee58f31daf">Engage app/data/batch owners</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ee5ea94a5976" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"54156f044c20">Manual</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d58d57231ead" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c52e11da4f62">Not evidenced</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"19136d7e23f7"><strong>Escalation bottlenecks (likely)</stron=
g></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9df9e36eb8ad">
<li local-id=3D"7eb12bb733c5">
<p local-id=3D"1f2c455655ee">If detection was customer-driven, escalation s=
tarts <strong>after impact</strong>, increasing containment time.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46a4eb286ce4">
<p local-id=3D"64a8deee4c16">Lack of a standardized =E2=80=9Cmessage suppre=
ssion=E2=80=9D runbook forces <strong>ad-hoc coordination</strong> across b=
atch + messaging teams.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3a8c3b53df69">
<h3 local-id=3D"ea8d441a3108" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-MTTR(Recovery)">MTTR (Recover=
y)</h3>
