<p local-id=3D"14e1bf0259d8"><strong>Required automated validation checks</=
strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8d6a7d2cf027">
<li local-id=3D"2ffeff4934b9">
<p local-id=3D"46dbe50f7c97"><strong>Pre-flight recipient count</strong> vs=
 historical baseline (block if above threshold).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6ae23b5fafa">
<p local-id=3D"b5b7241f4bf6"><strong>Template/channel eligibility validatio=
n</strong> (block if required flags missing/changed unexpectedly).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64bbad2e15e0">
<p local-id=3D"6a6cb4a87a80"><strong>Post-run reconciliation</strong>: expe=
cted vs actual sends, with automated sign-off criteria.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7e1f9e90dbe5">
<h2 local-id=3D"ee017fba9940" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-3)Lapu=E2=80=91Lapualignmenta=
nalysis">3) Lapu=E2=80=91Lapu alignment analysis</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"92365a946cfa" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-A)Observabilitycoverage(gapan=
alysis)">A) Observability coverage (gap analysis)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"28e4c553ff26">
<li local-id=3D"b225c0f41c06">
<p local-id=3D"98fbd685d7e2"><strong>Batch jobs:</strong> likely monitored =
for <em>failure</em>, but not for <em>bad outcomes</em> (wrong recipients).=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae3278f6ed99">
<p local-id=3D"81d91e27f6d6"><strong>Data integrity:</strong> missing contr=
ols to detect abnormal customer data updates feeding the batch.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8efcc59f0850">
<p local-id=3D"e9ddd8a6535c"><strong>Outbound messaging:</strong> missing e=
nd-to-end telemetry (volume, recipient uniqueness, template usage, suppress=
ion state).</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"75b2761dc0ae" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-B)Signalquality/noise">B) Sig=
nal quality / noise</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"dc8c4b699389">
<li local-id=3D"fb03b13e0205">
<p local-id=3D"82da3bafb465">No evidence of actionable alerts firing for th=
is scenario.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"63ae5f997558">
<p local-id=3D"d0f52b7488e7">Needed: <strong>few high-signal alerts</strong=
> (recipient spike, template spike, suppression disabled while volume abnor=
mal) rather than many low-value batch logs.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d5df63d2adc6" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-C)L1/L2operability(rapidrecov=
ery)">C) L1/L2 operability (rapid recovery)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"56a2cd006792">
<li local-id=3D"583b1eda64df">
<p local-id=3D"e72796a72ac7">Current state appears to require <strong>L3/da=
ta team involvement</strong> to correct data and ensure safety.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7730853eabb1">
<p local-id=3D"6368599c723f">Target state: L1/L2 can <strong>contain</stron=
g> (stop sends) and <strong>validate</strong> (volume back to baseline) usi=
ng a runbook + automation.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"bacf28632c46" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-D)Automationpotential(rankedb=
yimpact)">D) Automation potential (ranked by impact)</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e19971651e70">
<li local-id=3D"beef02c5fba4">
<p local-id=3D"ca96def7c215"><strong>Message suppression / circuit breaker<=
/strong> (highest impact): automatic stop when volume/recipient spike detec=
ted.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"23515afe75bb">
<p local-id=3D"55978b5adbf3"><strong>Pre-send validation gate</strong>: blo=
ck batch output if recipient count deviates beyond threshold.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f5ddc70251f">
<p local-id=3D"cfd1c51e563f"><strong>Automated rollback / quarantine</stron=
g> of the specific data update (where feasible).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3446e80a3b95">
<p local-id=3D"a78a6dc3277c"><strong>Auto-create incident + page correct te=
am</strong> when anomaly triggers (reduce time to engage).</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"402218ee0996">
<h2 local-id=3D"ca2e5f092a87" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-4)Rootcause+failurechain(caus=
alchain)">4) Root cause + failure chain (causal chain)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b50a542d062a"><strong>DATA CHANGE =E2=86=92 BATCH EXECUTION =
=E2=86=92 MESSAGE GENERATION =E2=86=92 CUSTOMER IMPACT</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"edd5c57b70b3">
<li local-id=3D"5b69f85b19a1">
<p local-id=3D"b072262e4324"><strong>Primary root cause (most likely):</str=
ong> Incorrect customer data update used by the batch, causing unintended r=
ecipients to be selected.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"115bf6829330">
<p local-id=3D"ff9cd322485d"><strong>Contributing factors (controls/monitor=
ing/process):</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9735178868b0">
<p local-id=3D"929a70c7553c">Missing <strong>recipient-volume guardrails</s=
trong> before sending.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee2574139022">
<p local-id=3D"fb9e2b829ccc">Missing <strong>data integrity checks</strong>=
 on the upstream update.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eed831682d78">
<p local-id=3D"4bbcb8a1d947">Weak <strong>traceability/logging</strong> bet=
ween batch records and outbound notifications (similar control gaps noted i=
n <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://manulife.service-now.com/probl=
em.do?sysparm_query=3Dnumber=3DPRB00023122" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>PRB000=
23122</strong></a>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6cd1bcac8bc4">
<p local-id=3D"d396bba26ff1"><strong>Where controls should have stopped pro=
pagation:</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"61b370ed1224">
<li local-id=3D"90499da6ed09">
<p local-id=3D"57a493e06cd5"><strong>At data change time:</strong> validati=
on + approval for high-risk mass-impact updates.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4d495389eee">
<p local-id=3D"0a248903b43e"><strong>At batch pre-flight:</strong> recipien=
t count anomaly detection (block).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c1ae71e7458">
<p local-id=3D"96f10c4bf90c"><strong>At message dispatch:</strong> circuit =
breaker / suppression when volume spikes.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"c075807e39ba">
<h2 local-id=3D"e95934413734" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-5)Recommendedactions(prioriti=
zed)">5) Recommended actions (prioritized)</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"ecf075567058" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-Tier1=E2=80=94Immediate(befor=
enextbatch)">Tier 1 =E2=80=94 Immediate (before next batch)</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d72667aab1e3">
<li local-id=3D"10c47f3a50c5">
<p local-id=3D"dae0e47c27bd"><strong>Enable a =E2=80=9Ckill switch=E2=80=9D=
 for outbound SMS/LINE</strong> (suppression toggle) with clear ownership a=
nd audit trail.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"582d5b23417a">
<p local-id=3D"da0cf0576a5c"><strong>Add a hard recipient-volume threshold<=
/strong> (block or require explicit approval when exceeded).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5b64dce8cb71">
<p local-id=3D"1924d51394a6"><strong>Run a pre-batch =E2=80=9Cdry run=E2=80=
=9D recipient count report</strong> and require sign-off when counts deviat=
e materially.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"2a8bc57ffd73" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-Tier2=E2=80=94Short-term(impr=
oveMTTD/MTTC/MTTR/MTTV)">Tier 2 =E2=80=94 Short-term (improve MTTD/MTTC/MTT=
R/MTTV)</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ec2656f824b2">
<li local-id=3D"fb04b2e0fccb">
<p local-id=3D"ef390ff3c63a"><strong>Automated alerting</strong> on outboun=
d message spikes (rate + unique recipients + template/channel).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbec93125110">
<p local-id=3D"450f4232e558"><strong>Correlation IDs + logging improvements=
</strong> (batch record =E2=86=92 notification ID =E2=86=92 provider respon=
se), aligned to recommendations seen in <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"=
https://manulife.service-now.com/problem.do?sysparm_query=3Dnumber=3DPRB000=
23122" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>PRB00023122</strong></a>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1dbbec6be6d6">
<p local-id=3D"25962b1fa397"><strong>Create an =E2=80=9COutbound Mis-send=
=E2=80=9D runbook</strong> (containment, comms, validation steps) and make =
it executable by L1/L2.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0dc2107c7fff">
<p local-id=3D"7efa00bb9512"><strong>Post-run reconciliation automation</st=
rong> (expected vs actual sends; auto-flag anomalies).</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"65c61909a97e" id=3D"IncidentAnalysis:UnintendedSMS/LINEMess=
agesSentto70,000CustomersDuetoDataUpdateError-Tier3=E2=80=94Strategic(Lapu=
=E2=80=91Lapualignment)">Tier 3 =E2=80=94 Strategic (Lapu=E2=80=91Lapu alig=
nment)</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"c1f407d25b07">
<li local-id=3D"4139870e06e2">
<p local-id=3D"9f4254aaa1bc"><strong>End-to-end observability</strong> for =
batch/data/messaging with SLO-style objectives (detect without customers, c=
ontain within minutes).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bb9ec79ac048">
<p local-id=3D"98188336dbd9"><strong>Data change governance for mass-impact=
 fields</strong> (validation rules, approvals, automated rollback/quarantin=
e).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d2166fed37c">
<p local-id=3D"9ec1eb1ec1bc"><strong>Automated incident creation + routing<=
/strong> from observability signals (reduce human latency).</p></li>
</ol>
